{
  "stem": "11144.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And walking in the forest for a couple of hours, all of a sudden, across, my mother saw his-- her brother walking, you know, walking the opposite way.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Well, you can imagine, I mean, that reunion, that there was a soul that, you know, family.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And that's how that started, hiding in the forest and going through this part of-- later on, while we were in forest and slept, you know, I mean, the-- the first, we slept on the ground and nothing to get changed in, and we were wet from the-- from the water and all that.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Then we found out how my father was killed, because somebody escaped from the mass gave.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It turned out that there was a mass grave that-- someplace on the outskirts of Ludwipol.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And apparently, they must have been taking the-- the Jews from the ghetto to dig these graves.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I didn't hear anything about it, but somebody either must have heard, [? though ?] people didn't speak about it because they were afraid to be shot maybe.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They-- they lined all these people, you know, at the-- the mass-- mass grave, and the German just shot all of them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Well, this-- this man that was telling us this story was not shot.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "His daughters next to him were shot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And when he saw that, he-- he jumped.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He-- he-- he fell to the grave, too, I mean.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And that misled the-- the-- the Germans, because they thought he was dead.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "In the middle of the night, he escaped-- he escaped the ghetto-- he escaped the-- the graves and whatever.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I think he survived, but I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "I don't remember his name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I don't know where they were-- I-- I know nothing about it, which is a shame.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
